    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain your <strong>tofu </strong>and pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Cut the <strong>tofu</strong> into strips</p><p>Coat the <strong>tofu</strong> in your <strong>curry powder</strong></p><p>Once softened, transfer the <strong>pepper </strong>and<strong> onion</strong> to a plate and return the pan to a medium-high heat (no need to clean!)</p>",
