    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>fine egg noodles</strong> to a large bowl, cover them with <strong>boiled water </strong>and stir for 10 secs to separate the noodles</p><p>Set aside to soak for 4 min</p><p>Drain the <strong>soaked noodles</strong> and return to the large bowl</p>",
