    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> lettuce wedges,</strong> <strong>cooked pepper </strong>and<strong> onion </strong>to the bowl with the <strong>drained noodles</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up (clean hands is the easiest way!)</p>",
